The dataset was obtained from the Department of Geography of the Ministry of Land Management, Urbanization and Construction in 2008 and unofficially updated in 2014 according to sub-decrees on administrative modifications. Data provided by WFP - VAM unit Cambodia.

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated reference name field 2. Found and fixed 2 Gap Errors. 3. Found and fixed small nesting errors with other admin layers 4. Found and fixed multipart sliver in unit "Romeas Haek". 5. Projection changed from undefined to 'GCS_WGS_1984'.
